@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.27) + (tmp + 0.88 + v1 + 0.56)) * 0.44)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.96)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.51)) * wp.exp((v0 + 0.69 - v1 + 0.67)))
    v2 = (0.47 * 0.98)
    v1 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.04 * v1 + 0.13)) - v1)
    data[tid] = v0
